  <h1><span>January 17, 1961: Farewell Address</span>
</h1>


    <div class="share-trigger-mobile"></div>
</div>
<div id="block-mainpagecontent">
  
    
      <article role="article" class="presidential-speech">

  
    

  <div class="ps-container video-container">
    <div class="presidential-speeches--sidebar">
      
<div  class="about-this-episode">
    <h3>About this speech</h3>
      
<div  class="about-this-episode--inner">
      
            <p class="president-name">Dwight D. Eisenhower</p>
      
            <p class="episode-date">January 17, 1961</p>
      
  <div class="speech-location-container">
    <span class="speech-label">Location</span>
              <span class="speech-loc">National Archives</span>
          </div>

            <div class="about-sidebar--intro"><p>Eisenhower again calls for peace, but, acknowledging that new crises arise, cautions the United States to maintain balance in its relations. He also also warns against the rising power of the military-industrial complex that could threaten the democratic process.</p>
</div>
      
  </div>
  </div>
    </div>

    <div class="presidential-speeches--body-wrapper">
     <a href="/the-presidency/presidential-speeches" class="back-to-listing--cta">Presidential Speeches</a> <span class="nav-separator">|</span> <label class="presidential-speeches--label">Dwight D. Eisenhower Presidency</label>
      <h2 class="presidential-speeches--title"><span>January 17, 1961: Farewell Address</span>
</h2>
      
<div  class="presidential-speeches--body">
      
            <div class="presidential-speeches--audio"><div class="audio-player">
    <audio height="100" src="https://web2.millercenter.org/speeches/audio/spe_1961_0117_eisenhower.mp3"
                            data-wave_color="#888888"
                                        data-prog_color="#E65400"
                            ></audio>
    <div class="controls">
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-back">
            <i class="fa fa-step-backward"></i>
            Backward
        </button>

        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-play play">
